<wpt lat="39.1155539228" lon="-110.854119549"><ele>1603.0</ele><name>River crossing</name><desc>Fuller Bottom ford of the San Rafael River (Upper San Rafael River WMA, BLM Fuller Bottom road = NF-3516 / BLM 6767, becomes Little Wedge Road / BLM 629 south of the crossing). Added per group request -- water crossings desirable for overlanders.</desc><sym>water</sym></wpt>
<wpt lat="39.12445" lon="-110.75133"><name>[CAMP PRIMARY] May 5 (Tue) - Day 3: Family Butte -&gt; Wedge (breather) - Wedge Overlook Campsite #5 (GPX) - cluster anchor (#3/#4/#5/#6/#7)</name><desc>$15/site honor system | None | First-come only. Tight #3-#7 cluster on the west rim. Scout ahead during any Buckhorn stop; claim 3-4 adjacent sites for the group. | Access: Wedge Rd spur off Buckhorn Draw Rd</desc><sym>Campground</sym></wpt>
<wpt lat="39.12423" lon="-110.74498"><name>[CAMP PRIMARY-CLUSTER] May 5 (Tue) - Day 3: Family Butte -&gt; Wedge (breather) - Wedge Overlook Campsite #3</name><desc>Designated site in the primary cluster anchored at Wedge Overlook Campsite #5 (GPX) - cluster anchor (#3/#4/#5/#6/#7)</desc><sym>Campground</sym></wpt>
<wpt lat="39.12748" lon="-110.74781"><name>[CAMP PRIMARY-CLUSTER] May 5 (Tue) - Day 3: Family Butte -&gt; Wedge (breather) - Wedge Overlook Campsite #4</name><desc>Designated site in the primary cluster anchored at Wedge Overlook Campsite #5 (GPX) - cluster anchor (#3/#4/#5/#6/#7)</desc><sym>Campground</sym></wpt>
<wpt lat="39.12254" lon="-110.75204"><name>[CAMP PRIMARY-CLUSTER] May 5 (Tue) - Day 3: Family Butte -&gt; Wedge (breather) - Wedge Overlook Campsite #6</name><desc>Designated site in the primary cluster anchored at Wedge Overlook Campsite #5 (GPX) - cluster anchor (#3/#4/#5/#6/#7)</desc><sym>Campground</sym></wpt>
<wpt lat="39.12563" lon="-110.75521"><name>[CAMP PRIMARY-CLUSTER] May 5 (Tue) - Day 3: Family Butte -&gt; Wedge (breather) - Wedge Overlook Campsite #7</name><desc>Designated site in the primary cluster anchored at Wedge Overlook Campsite #5 (GPX) - cluster anchor (#3/#4/#5/#6/#7)</desc><sym>Campground</sym></wpt>
<wpt lat="39.10857" lon="-110.70223"><name>[CAMP BACKUP-A] May 5 (Tue) - Day 3: Family Butte -&gt; Wedge (breather) - Wedge Overlook Camp #1 (GPX) - east-rim site</name><desc>$15/site honor system | None | East-side rim site. Good sunrise exposure but farther from the iconic overlook. | Access: Wedge Rd east spur</desc><sym>Campground</sym></wpt>
<wpt lat="39.11221" lon="-110.73341"><name>[CAMP BACKUP-B] May 5 (Tue) - Day 3: Family Butte -&gt; Wedge (breather) - Wedge Overlook Camp #2 (GPX) - east-rim site</name><desc>$15/site honor system | None | East-side rim site midway between #1 and the overlook. | Access: Wedge Rd east spur</desc><sym>Campground</sym></wpt>
<wpt lat="39.11674" lon="-110.75523"><name>[CAMP BACKUP-C] May 5 (Tue) - Day 3: Family Butte -&gt; Wedge (breather) - Wedge Overlook Campsite #8 (GPX) - southern outlier</name><desc>$15/site honor system | None | Extends the cluster if we need one extra site, or stand-alone backup. | Access: Wedge Rd spur, ~900 m before the main overlook turn-off</desc><sym>Campground</sym></wpt>
<wpt lat="39.16753" lon="-110.73766"><name>[CAMP LAST-RESORT] May 5 (Tue) - Day 3: Family Butte -&gt; Wedge (breather) - Buckhorn Draw Campsite 1 (GPX) - developed loop</name><desc>$15 ind / $50 group | Vault toilets, fire rings, tables | 32 sites + 7 group sites. First-come. ~8 km S of Wedge. | Access: Buckhorn Draw Rd</desc><sym>Campground</sym></wpt>
<wpt lat="39.0955288221" lon="-110.7490264424"><ele>1917.0</ele><name>DP - Wedge Overlook</name><desc>End-of-day highlight</desc><sym>binoculars</sym></wpt>
